<h1 class="hero-h">What Is Claude Team? <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">Claude for B2B teams of 5-150.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Claude Team is the right tier for most $5M-$50M B2B companies adopting Claude. Here's exactly what's in it, what it costs, and how it differs from Pro and Enterprise.</p>
<div class="tldr"><div class="tldr-l">Short answer</div><p class="tldr-p">Claude Team is Anthropic's mid-tier business plan at $30/user/month, designed for teams of roughly 5-150. Includes shared Projects, admin controls, no training on inputs, and centralized billing. The right starting point for most B2B mid-market AI rollouts.</p></div>
</div></div>

<div style="background:#0A1A0A;border-top:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
<div style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:0.78rem;color:#8FAF8F;">
<div>By <a href="/about" style="color:#F0FFF0;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Bill Colbert</a> · <span style="color:#4A6A4A;">Founder, Treetop Growth Strategy</span></div>
<div style="color:#4A6A4A;">Published May 2026 · <a href="/content-library" style="color:#8FAF8F;text-decoration:none;">More from the library</a></div>
</div>
</div>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">What's included in Claude Team</h2><ul class="ul"><li><strong>Claude Sonnet</strong> as default model; Opus available per conversation.</li><li><strong>Claude Projects:</strong> shared, with team-wide knowledge and instructions.</li><li><strong>Admin console</strong> for user management, usage analytics, and billing.</li><li><strong>No training on inputs:</strong> your conversations and Projects are not used to train Anthropic models.</li><li><strong>Centralized billing:</strong> single invoice for the whole team.</li><li><strong>Higher usage limits</strong> than the Pro tier.</li></ul></div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<h2 class="h2">Claude Team pricing and plan comparison</h2>
<p class="body">Three tiers exist: Free, Pro, Team, and Enterprise. Here is how they compare on the dimensions that matter most for business buyers.</p>
