<p class="body" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">At 10 seats billed annually, Claude Team costs $3,600/year. At 50 seats it's $18,000/year. Both are self-serve with no contract required.</p>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">Why Team is the right starting point for most B2B mid-market companies</h2><ul class="ul"><li>Cost-effective at $30/seat for the capability you get.</li><li>Has the business-critical features: no training on data, admin controls, shared Projects.</li><li>No long sales process. Sign up and provision the same day.</li><li>Easy to upgrade to Enterprise if you outgrow it.</li><li>Shared Projects let your team build a shared AI brain: one set of instructions, one knowledge base, consistent outputs.</li><li>Admin console gives you visibility into usage before you scale spend.</li></ul></div></section>
<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">When to step up to Enterprise</h2><ul class="ul"><li>You need SSO (especially Okta, Azure AD) integration.</li><li>You need SCIM provisioning.</li><li>You need audit logging beyond what Team offers.</li><li>You handle PHI and need a Business Associate Agreement.</li><li>You need custom data retention policies.</li><li>You have 150+ seats.</li></ul></div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner"><h2 class="h2">FAQ</h2>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">How much does Claude Team cost per user?</h3><p class="faq-qa">$30 per user per month billed annually. The minimum purchase is 5 seats, so the lowest entry cost is $150 per month.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Does Claude Team train on my data?</h3><p class="faq-qa">No. Inputs to Claude Team are not used to train Anthropic models.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">What is the minimum number of seats?</h3><p class="faq-qa">5 seats. Below that, individual Pro accounts at $20/month make more sense.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">How quickly can I provision Claude Team?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Same day. Sign up via Anthropic, invite team members, start using.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Can I get a BAA on Claude Team?</h3><p class="faq-qa">BAAs are on Enterprise only. If you handle PHI, upgrade to Enterprise.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">What is the difference between Claude Team and Claude Enterprise?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Team is self-serve at $30/seat with no contract. Enterprise adds SSO, SCIM, advanced audit logs, a BAA for HIPAA, and custom data retention. Enterprise requires a direct Anthropic sales conversation.</p></div>
<div class="faq-q"><h3 class="faq-qh">Can I expand to Enterprise later?</h3><p class="faq-qa">Yes, smoothly. Anthropic supports the upgrade path from Team to Enterprise.</p></div>
</div></section>

